---
title: Paneer Tikka Masala Tacos with Roasted Cauliflower and Pickled Radishes
description: Lightly spiced chunks of paneer are seared then tossed in our tikka masala sauce for an unforgettable Indian-style taco experience. Roasted cauliflower drizzled with honey adds a touch of sweetness and the pickled radishes give a delicious acidic kick!
